Metronome cracks—zip—we redraw skylines in cold chrome,  
Twin reactors screaming—two thrones, same home.  
Self-made? Respect—but we’re self-forged, stone-to-storm;  
Deadlines into launchpads, trendlines into form.  
Click-clack syntax, cat’s-cradle on the kick;  
We ghostwrite gravity, make heavy feel slick.  
멈춰? 생각해—nah, 가자—beam in the slipstream;  
