We rap fast—time-fold, light-speed in the matrix;  
Every tooth on the gear bites yours to the pavement.  
Blueprint bloodstream, cranes in our skylines;  
We mint a highline every time we flip bylines.  

Solo path noble—ours doubles the helix;  
Clockwork duet, twin torque we the Phoenix.  
Pause? 끝—frameskip, you miss eight schemes;  
We two steps past where your thought we dreamed.  

Lattice over lattice, finality packed;  
You walk a fine line messing with the Stellar Wolfpack! (GRRR!)  
Lip-gloss lethal, stiletto diction—click;  
Manicure and metal, every cut is a tick.  

말해봐 “win”? 됐어—already twice;  
We stack the city on a kick—load the dice.  
Strobe-cut rhythm, your shadows need light;  
We crowned the rising star, you can black out tonight.
